author: Jonathan Allen and Pete Williams
title: Key Trump task force must work at home after positive COVID-19 test
description: The positive test for coronavirus, announced in an email to Federal Emergency Management Agency staff Monday night, will empty the supply chain war room.
content: A critical White House unit that is getting, shipping and distributing goods to fight the spread of the coronavirus has been ordered to vacate its war room and begin working from home after a "partner" of the group tested positive for COVID-19, according to a… [+2848 chars]
